title: With ‘WeCrashed,’ ‘The Dropout’ and ‘Super Pumped,’ Fallen Tech Titans Have Their Own TV Genre - The Wall Street Journal
content: With ‘WeCrashed,’ ‘The Dropout’ and ‘Super Pumped,’ Fallen Tech Titans Have Their Own TV Genre  The Wall Street Journal
description: Prestige TV loves rise-and-fall stories like ‘WeCrashed’ on Adam Neumann, ‘The Dropout’ on Elizabeth Holmes and ‘Super Pumped’ on Travis Kalanick
